{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"69ed05900f","title":"接见军队领导干部时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a8da1e616c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"69ed05900f","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"30ad9a64e1","type":"title","text":"接见军队领导干部时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4edad40b7f","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕闹，闹得越大、越长，越好。七闹八闹，总会闹出名堂来的，可以闹清楚。不管怎么闹，不要怕，越怕鬼越来。但也不要开枪，什么时候开枪也是不好的。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebda064af7","type":"paragraph","text":"全国大闹不可能。那里有脓包，有细菌，总要爆发的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21654ba6cc","type":"paragraph","text":"南京街上闹得很厉害，我越看越高兴。闹得第三派那么多人，反对内战，反对武斗，这很好嘛！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34a52bae97","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥：有人讲第三派是走第三条道路的。）","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8c17b600d5","type":"paragraph","text":"哪有什么第三条道路呀！人家要大联合，大批判，你要诱导嘛！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}